        <summary>
            Indicates whether content compression is enabled on AzureFrontDoor.
            Default value is false. If compression is enabled, content will be
            served as compressed if user requests for a compressed version.
            Content won't be compressed on AzureFrontDoor when requested
            content is smaller than 1 byte or larger than 1 MB.
